  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Buildable<T>
    Markup Interface for Buildable Objects
    Builders Must Have:
    Empty Default Constructor with Private Accessor Contains Same Fields of Implementation Class Constructor with Required Fields All Setter Fields Must Return {this} or Current Builder
    Persistable
    Markup Interface for Persistable Entities
    Implements this for works with
    SimpleEntityConverter and AnotherEntityConverter in JSF
    Traceable
    Markup Interface for Traceable Entities
